Optional default (only if you want it)

If some events omit when, you can default them to both insert+update once, when loading:

for (EventConfig.Event e : cfg.events) {
  if (e.when == null || e.when.isEmpty()) {
    e.when = java.util.Arrays.asList("insert","update");
  }
}

(Place that in your config loader after deserialization.)

